{"tid":1382540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你連三萬人嘅委任証都管唔好","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:45:58.000Z","uid":58434,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f866203a2320a1c2e03a227261c63a280196c458","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"你連三萬人嘅委任証都管唔好無謂再為自己辯護，更唔好撚再為700萬市民服務<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n精明嘅你就好辭職，安份守己做你毅進仔拎毅進嘅人工，<br />\n<br />\n為咗你嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">家人</span></span>好好地平平淡淡生活落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇清楚係三萬人對二百萬人以上</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地係不死，我地係薪火相傳，會將清算嘅精神帶到全球各地每家每戶至每一代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要忘記你地已經同黑幫掛咗勾，你地嘅污名係一世<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗單嘢我地香港大眾市民絕對係唔撚放過你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以為著制服就係絕對正義，絕對嘅專業？拎住槍拎住棍就係執行職務？就唔好阻你做嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地要啲市民背翻條警例去督鳩住你頭做嘢，肉鳩酸到，你地必需要承應你地係低學歷，無能力去做一份呢份咁高轉數嘅工作，你只係高估咗自己嘅能力</span>"},{"pid":"84c7469095c793d1cecf1efde2d1a97591c7f6d7","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada039e25f788ae415ced7f719383b15861f74c","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac5c8dbaed47a2d33259c0525cda4a258b0352","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d0ce822316d9dce4520572b3ce142b294152fa","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"不灰心"},{"pid":"ecb0cc54e5f5a9add86d1c027ad4e06d60b48359","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"不灰心"},{"pid":"30da98d495935c3b56f1080e6b48ea3d7dc782c0","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"不灰心"},{"pid":"ba9e95bc1bc6705f37cc8d9303ed0057f7c07ebf","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87da876236dbb1922823a6db7bcb0f587371e937","tid":1382540,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}